      "writtenOn": "2018-01-25T19:00:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "this will happen if the file is not in a git repo. I think we should not prohibit bqschemaupdater usage with proto files not in git. In general, below, let\u0027s just use the filename \"foo.proto\" if gitiles URL could not be determined. This is consistent with .go files generated from .proto files.",
